19#include "ResultPoint.h"
20
21#include <array>
22
23namespace ZXing {
24namespace OneD {
25namespace RSS {
26
27class FinderPattern
28{
29 int _value = -1;
30 int _start = -1;
31 int _end = -1;
32 std::array<ResultPoint, 2> _points;
33
34public:
35 FinderPattern() = default;
36 FinderPattern(int value, int start, int end, const std::array<ResultPoint, 2>& points) :
37 _value(value), _start(start), _end(end), _points(points) {}
38
39 bool isValid() const {
40 return _value >= 0;
41 }
42
43 int value() const {
44 return _value;
45 }
46
47 int startPos() const {
48 return _start;
49 }
50
51 int endPos() const {
52 return _end;
53 }
54
55 const std::array<ResultPoint, 2>& points() const {
56 return _points;
57 }
58};
59
60} // RSS
61} // OneD
62} // ZXing
